### Admin Login Endpoint Test
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5080/api
@adminEmail = admin@mura.com
@adminPassword = 12345678

### 1. Admin Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

### 2. Regular User Login (for comparison)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Failed Admin Login - Wrong Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 4. Failed Admin Login - Non-admin User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

